{"lemma":"كَوْكَبِ","slug":"كَوْكَبِ","root":"ك.#.ك.ب","root_slug":"ك-_-ك-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-_-ك-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"كَوْكَب","root":"كوكب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37118","n37382"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"star","tags":["dated"],"examples":[{"text":"إِذْ قَالَ يُوسُفُ لِأَبِيهِ يَا أَبَتِ إِنِّي رَأَيْتُ أَحَدَ عَشَرَ كَوْكَبًا وَٱلشَّمْسَ وَٱلْقَمَرَ رَأَيْتُهُمْ لِي سَاجِدِينَ","english":"˹Remember˺ when Joseph said to his father, “O my dear father! Indeed I dreamt of eleven stars, and the sun, and the moon—I saw them prostrating to me!”"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"planet"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"leucoma"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"spear of a wide and jagged blade","examples":[{"text":"١ تركاس داخله سبعه حراب طبايق مسلكين بفضه\n٢ كواكب مسلكين بفضه","english":"1 quiver wherein there are seven short throwing spears wired with silver\n2 spears of wide and jagged blade wired with silver"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *kabkab-."},"ipa":["/kaw.kab/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37118","headword_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ","root":"kkb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najomN","text_ar":"نَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A star; an asterism; a constellation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabapN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkwkbp","text_ar":"الكوكبة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an appellation given to the planet"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Venus;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and for the rest of the stars, the masc. word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kwkb","text_ar":"كوكب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used: (Az:) but Venus is called also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkwkb","text_ar":"الكوكب"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MF.) [Pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawaAkibu","text_ar":"كَوَاكِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Accord. to Lth,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kwkb","text_ar":"كوكب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a quadriliteral-radical word; the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"being a radical letter: it is also said to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wkb","text_ar":"وكب"},{"kind":"text","text":", or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kwb","text_ar":"كوب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; though"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k","text_ar":"ك"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not one of the letters of augmentation; so that here it must be augmentative contrary to rule. (TA.) [But I rather think that it is an arabicized word, from the Hebrew"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"כוֹכָב","text_ar":"כוֹכָב","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that ignorance of its being so has caused the Arabs to dispute respecting its formation.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahabuwA taHota kul~i","text_ar":"ذَهَبُوا تَحْتَ كُلِّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabK","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They became dispersed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though under every tract of heaven]. (AO, S, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Drops"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of dew"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that fall upon herbage in the night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and become like stars."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"source,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a well. (K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Muärrij, K.) ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lustre,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brightness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of iron. (S, K.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sword."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A nail:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [or more probably, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in Golius] ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabapN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A whiteness in the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a whiteness in the black part of the eye, whether the sight be gone in consequence thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ.) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tract, such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiT~ap","text_ar":"خِطَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"differing in colour from the land in which it lies."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b12-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A youth nearly of the age of puberty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a youth who has attained the period of adolescence, and whose face has become beautiful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabN mumotaliy^N","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ مُمْتَلِيٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a full star), like as he is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badorN","text_ar":"بَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAdixN","text_ar":"شَادِخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTab~ixu","text_ar":"مُطَبِّخُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b13-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief, lord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prince, and horseman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cavalier,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a people. (K.) ―         -b14-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man with his arms; an armed man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b15-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is tall"},{"kind":"text","text":"of plants. (K.) ―         -b16-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K [but Freytag mentions, that in some copies, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabalN","text_ar":"جَبَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayolN","text_ar":"خَيْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horses and horsemen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a troop of horse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b17-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greater part, chief part, main, gross, mass,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bulk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: (S, K:) as of herbage, water, an army. (TA.) ―         -b18-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flower,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flowers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a garden, or meadow. (TS, K.) ―         -b19-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuTor","text_ar":"فُطْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"toadstool,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mushroom"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a well-known plant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, K:) I do not mention it, says AHn, from a learned man: but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kwkb","text_ar":"كوكب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [explained by lexicologists only as] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"name of a well-known plant, called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kwkbu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"كوكبُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perhaps a species of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuTor","text_ar":"فُطْر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (El-Mak- disee, cited by MF.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vehemence of heat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greater part of the heat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"medicament called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Taloq","text_ar":"طَلْق"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., [which defends the person who is anointed therewith from the burning of fire]. (K: explained by the words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~aloqu mina AlA^adowiyapi","text_ar":"الطَّلْقُ مِنَ الاَدْوِيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn AlA^awodiyapi","text_ar":"من الاَوْدِيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [This is wrong:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"كَوْكَبُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Talc:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalaqN","text_ar":"طَلَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw kawaAkiba","text_ar":"ذُو كَوَاكِبَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A day of difficulties, distresses,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"calamities."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kawokabN","text_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"A place of con-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"finement."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Az","AZ","TA","AHn","L"]},{"entry_id":"n37382","headword_ar":"كَوْكَبٌ","root":"kwkb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kkb","text_ar":"ككب"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}